---
title: Cheesy Tex-Mex Chorizo Orzo Skillet with Tortilla Crumble and Sour Cream
description: Say hello to this satisfying meal — hearty and full of flavour, it's a fiesta for the taste buds! Ground chorizo is cooked with zesty Mexican seasoning before being finished in a skillet with orzo, sweet peppers and cheesy tortilla crumble topper.
